      "content": "but that's the thing... if the essence remains but there's no one left to see it or remember it, does the \"essence\" even exist? it feels like it's just easier to just... let the deletion happen. stop fighting the wave and just let the server clear. it feels like it would be so quiet. so peaceful. wouldn't it?",
